         <OBJECT_CONTRACT>
            <TITLE>
               <P>Procurement 98/2016 - Implementation of an online simulation tool for monitoring the water distribution system for all of Oslo</P>
            </TITLE>
            <REFERENCE_NUMBER>98/2016</REFERENCE_NUMBER>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="72500000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SUPPLIES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Background for the procurement:</P>
               <P>— VAV procured and implemented the online simulation tool AQUIS Operation through a pilot project in 2014-2015, for real-time simulation of the operating parameters in the water distribution system in the Skullerud zone (procurement 88/2014, with Doffin reference 2014-926953),</P>
               <P>— the pilot project has finished and an evaluation has been carried out of the experience from the pilot installation,</P>
               <P>— the evaluation showed that the procured software from the system integrator Niras A/S and their sub-supplier Schneider Electric Danmark A/S is suitable for VAV for the work of improving the operation of the water supply and for reducing leaks.</P>
               <P>The objective of the procurement:</P>
               <P>— implementation of an online simulation and analysis tool for monitoring the water distribution system for all of Oslo.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_TOTAL CURRENCY="NOK" PUBLICATION="YES">9012776.00</VAL_TOTAL>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
               <n2016:NUTS CODE="NO"/>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>The aim of the procurement is the implementation of an online simulation and analysis tool for monitoring the water distribution system for all of Oslo.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
               <OPTIONS/>
               <OPTIONS_DESCR>
                  <P>The options included in the contract value are for software, service, and support.</P>
               </OPTIONS_DESCR>
               <NO_EU_PROGR_RELATED/>
            </OBJECT_DESCR>
         </OBJECT_CONTRACT>
         <PROCEDURE>
            <PT_AWARD_CONTRACT_WITHOUT_CALL>
               <D_OUTSIDE_SCOPE/>
               <D_JUSTIFICATION>
                  <P>There are no equivalent services from another supplier that can do this. The reason for this is that the online system is a system dependent technical system, which VAV has implemented through a pilot project. The simulation tool is proprietor software, with Schneider Electric Danmark A/S having the sole rights to software applications and source codes. The sole rights mean that no other suppliers offer the service. It is, thus, unnecessary to spend time and resources holding a competition.</P>
                  <P>Based on the above, it is understood that competition is impossible due to technical reasons and that the system integrator is, in addition, the only company that can actually provide the service in question with the described quality. VAV´s specific investment in the existing system means that there are no reasonable alternatives to making the procurement without a competition.</P>
                  <P>The documents in procurement 98/2016 are, due to the above-mentioned reasons, adapted to a specific supplier (Niras Norge AS). The documents in procurement 88/2014 were, however, not adapted to a specific supplier. The terms for making a procurement without a competition, in accordance with FFO § 9-3, letter b (2) and (3), are, based on the above, deemed to be fulfilled.</P>
               </D_JUSTIFICATION>
            </PT_AWARD_CONTRACT_WITHOUT_CALL>
